{"type":"message","id":"713f3022","parentId":"a10a23d0","timestamp":"2026-03-23T20:51:36.577Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1fpaifvpuogk_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5185\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2396\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\n[mutation proposed] a\n[master 2921d24] pulse: 2026-03-23 165102\n 7 files changed, 338 insertions(+), 141 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 165102.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 165102.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 164101.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 165102 - The TIC Experiment is the critical next step for Phase 1 advancement, but there's no implementation yet. The hypothesis is clear: causal structure IS invariant structure, and we need to test this on the pulse logs."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"sharp-harbor","total":10,"totalLines":10,"totalChars":697,"truncated":false,"exitCode":0,"name":"powershell C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774299096575}}
